Sparrow3d:
* creating an IRC thread for one server
	* connects to server
	* responses to ping
* sending /messages to the thread
* creating child channels if something is joined
* getting a list of changes since last time as list
	* context (channel, server, error, etc.)
	* content

Sissi:
* First view server config
* L + up => server view
* L + left/right => switch between different servers/channels
* GUI class system
	* window operator class
		* register window pairs (!)
			* main view
			* options view
		* deregister window pairs (!)
		* changing between views
		* calling window calc function
		* drawing the necessary windows (+ changes)
	* window class
		* surface to draw to
		* size
		* virtual updateWindow();
		* virtual calc();
